text: KDOT (map legend) Hickok is an unincorporated community in Grant County, Kansas, United States. It lies in eastern Lincoln TownshipCensus Bureau map, combined with KDOT map along U.S. Route 160, 7 miles (11 km) east of the county seat of Ulysses.Official Kansas highway map ==References== ==Further reading== ==External links== * Grant County Maps: Current, Historic, KDOT Category:Unincorporated communities in Grant County, Kansas Category:Unincorporated communities in Kansas
